# Portable defaults work without editing: the connector falls back to
# .connector-state/ for tiny no-network fixture runs.
#
# For larger local runs, set these to external storage. On this host a suitable
# example is /srv/abyss-machine/storage/connectors/aoa-xda-connector, but public
# clones should choose their own paths.

# CONNECTOR_FAMILY_ROOT=/path/to/connector-databases
# CONNECTOR_INSTANCE_ROOT=${CONNECTOR_FAMILY_ROOT}/aoa-xda-connector
# CONNECTOR_DATA_ROOT=${CONNECTOR_INSTANCE_ROOT}/data
# CONNECTOR_CACHE_ROOT=${CONNECTOR_INSTANCE_ROOT}/cache
# CONNECTOR_ARTIFACT_ROOT=${CONNECTOR_INSTANCE_ROOT}/artifacts
